### Test authenticated summarization (requires real JWT token from Supabase)
### To get a token: 
### 1. Go to http://localhost:3002
### 2. Sign in with Supabase
### 3. Open browser DevTools > Application > Local Storage
### 4. Find the access_token and copy it below
# POST http://localhost:3000/summarizer
# Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_REAL_TOKEN_HERE
# 
# {
#   "url": "https://youtu.be/B-ukcWJzXwc?si=LAZDRrVvWzujroJi"
# }